name: Business Objective
description: A strategic goal the enterprise aims to achieve

name: Strategic Initiative
description: A program designed to realize business objectives

name: Business Capability
description: An ability that an organization possesses to achieve a specific purpose

name: Change Initiative
description: A transformation effort affecting processes, capabilities, or systems

name: Risk
description: A potential event that could negatively affect change outcomes

name: Benefit
description: A measurable improvement resulting from change

name: Stakeholder
description: An individual or group affected by or involved in the change

name: Deliverable
description: An output produced as part of a change initiative

name: Process
description: A series of steps to achieve a business result

name: Service
description: A function provided to stakeholders or systems
